# Extensibility design

- **Interfaces**: Predicate, options, and report types are abstracted so new predicates and options can be added with minimal core changes.
- **Future extensions** (design memo only for MVP): anyOf/or, not(), matchAll/full semantics, async validators. Keep extension points in types/interfaces.
- **hasLanguage(locale)**: MVP supports "ko" only; add locale → pattern map for "ja", "zh", etc. when extending.
- When adding a new predicate: prefer one file per predicate, register name + testFn + optional patternSource; avoid changing core evaluation flow.
